author: Kindsey Bernhard
title: Relive last night’s scary win through Twitter
text:
— Andrew Cassady (@ACassady_KSR) October 4, 2015 Thank you Dorian, for saving this program from unimaginable embarrassment. 
— Tyler Thompson (@MrsTylerKSR) October 4, 2015 Mr.Baker, you are one bad man! #BBN 
— Karl-Anthony Towns (@KarlTowns) October 4, 2015 Never doubted.(Kinda doubted.) 
— Drew Franklin (@DrewFranklinKSR) October 4, 2015 YOU MEAN I'M GONNA HALTHF TO WATSCH 20 MORE OVERTHIME MINUTESH OF THISH THIT?! Come on, NODER DAME ISH ON! #EKYvsUK #BBN 
— Lou Holtz (@FakeLouHoltzKSR) October 4, 2015 I think Dorian Baker should run against Andy Barr 
— Matt Jones (@KySportsRadio) October 4, 2015 If Dorian Baker played for UofL, he's earned Maid Marian being sent to his room tonight
